quran[18{c,v,t}:
52,32,kiya un ki aqlain un ko yahi sikhati hain. balkay yeh log hain hi shareer
52,33,kiya ( kufar ) kehte hain ke un paighambar ne quran az khud bana liya hai baat yeh hai ke yeh ( khuda par ) imaan nahi rakhtay
52,34,agar yeh sachey hain to aisa kalaam bana to layein
52,35,kiya yeh kisi ke peda kiye baghair hi peda hogaye hain. ya yeh khud ( apne tain ) peda karne walay hain
52,36,ya unhon ne asmano aur zameen ko pedakiya hai? ( nahi ) balkay yeh yaqeen hi nahi rakhtay
52,37,kiya un ke paas tumahray perwar-digaar ke khazanay hain. ya yeh ( kahin ke ) Darogha hain ?
52,38,ya un ke paas koi seerhi hai jis par ( charh kar aasman se baatein ) sun atay hain. to jo sun aata hai woh Sarih sanad dukhaay
52,39,kiya khuda ki to betiyan aur tumahray betay
52,40,( ae paighambar )kiya tum un se sila mangte ho ke un par tawwan ka boojh par raha hai
52,41,ya un ke paas ghaib ( ka ilm ) hai ke woh usay likh letay hain
52,42,kiya yeh koi daon karna chahtay hain to kafir to khud daon mein anay walay hain
52,43,kiya khuda ke siwa un ka koi aur mabood hai? khuda un ke shareek bananay se pak hai
52,44,aur agar yeh aasman se ( azaab ) ka koi tukda girta howa dekhen to kahin ke yeh gaarha baadal hai
52,45,"pas un ko chore do yahan taq ke woh roz jis mein woh be hosh kardiye jayen ge, samnay aajay"
52,46,jis din un ka koi daon kuch bhi kaam nah aeye aur nah un ko ( kahin se ) madad hi miley
52,47,aur zaalmon ke liye is ke siwa aur azaab bhi hai lekin un mein ke aksar nahi jantay
52,48,aur tum apne perwar-digaar ke hukum ke intzaar mein sabr kiye raho. tum to hamari aankhon ke samnay ho aur jab uttha karo to apne perwar-digaar ki tareef ke sath tasbeehkiya karo
52,49,aur raat ke baaz auqaat mein bhi aur sitaron ke ghuroob honay ke baad bhi is ki تنزیہkiya karo
